="html">&lt;p>;Lofree Flow 是一款低调的键盘，打字和听起来都像全高键盘。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23965283/lofree-flow -low-profile-keyboard-review&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23965283/lofree-flow-low-profile-keyboard-review" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23965283/lofree-flow-low-profile-keyboard-review</id><author><name>丹·塞弗特</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-17T09:00:00-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-17T09:00:00-05:00</updated><title>凯迪拉克新款 Optiq 紧凑型电动 SUV 将是最便宜的电动汽车</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;橙色凯迪拉克 SUV，顶部涂成黑色，位于玻璃面板建筑前&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/4ZB7B8Q9Mqb1FQO3FCZZADJjXNE=/0x0:6325x4217/1310x873/cdn .vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72875439/MY24_CADILLAC_OPTIQ_SPORT_GMCA0740.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Optiq，你到底有多便宜？&lt;/em>; |图片：凯迪拉克&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;X2AwUB&quot;>;凯迪拉克宣布推出一款名为 Optiq 的新型电动汽车，据称该车型将“作为该汽车制造商在美国的电动汽车产品线的切入点”。此前，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23522467/cadillac-lyriq-ev-review-specs-photos-price&quot;>;售价 64,000 美元的凯迪拉克 Lyriq&lt;/a>; 是该汽车制造商最便宜的电动汽车选择，因此 Optiq 的起价可能会低于 60,000 美元，尽管该公司尚未公布这方面的任何细节。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;EZnEfP&quot;>;事实上，凯迪拉克尚未提供任何细节无论如何，包括关键规格，如电池范围、尺寸、动力系统选项，如是否具有 AWD 标准、充电速度等。尽管未经证实，Optiq 很可能基于通用汽车的 Ultium 电动汽车平台构建。我们所知道的是它至少会采用橙色，具有正面设计......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/17/23964593 /cadillac-optiq-ev-compact-suv-teaser&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/17/23964593/cadillac-optiq-ev-compact-suv-teaser" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/17/23964593/cadillac-optiq-ev-compact-suv-teaser</id><author><name>奥马尔·沙基尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-17T09:00:00-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-17T09:00:00-05:00</updated><title> Tumblr 在变小上下了大赌注</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;粉色和紫色背景上的 Tumblr 徽标&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/V9s3NWknMlUhre6uynnq28E1DjU=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn. com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72875398/STK137_Tumblr_K_Radtke_01.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;插图：边缘&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;社交网络未能实现其新所有者设定的增长目标2019 年。但它们是否与 Tumblr 最擅长的领域兼容？&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/17/23964580/tumblr-downscaling-smaller-social -media-site&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/17/23964580/tumblr-downscaling-smaller-social-media-site" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2023/11/17/23964580/tumblr-downscaling-smaller-social-media-site</id><author><name>阿莱格拉·罗森伯格</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-17T09:00:00-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-17T09:00:00-05:00</updated><title>亚马逊设备上黑色星期五早期最佳优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;桌子上有一个紫色的 Echo Pop 智能音箱，周围环绕着 Ring Pop 糖果。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/ST7cEe9-ENgx3UPQ3QPeAxAp9c8=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72875400/236685_Amazon_Echo_Pop_JTuohy_0 001.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;亚马逊奇特的 Echo Pop 是一份不错的经济实惠的礼物......尤其是当它的售价低于 20 美元时。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Jennifer Pattison Tuohy / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;nkySMF&quot;>;亚马逊再次对自家设备进行大促销，这似乎是今年第十亿次。然而，这一次是为了纪念&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23939216/black-friday-guide-cyber-monday-tech-gadgets-2023&quot;>;黑色星期五&lt;/a>;，尽管大型购物活动要到 11 月 24 日才会真正举行。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;iNWzPb&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem -component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;The Verge 2023 年节日礼物指南&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/ 23939057/holiday-gift-guide-2023-best-ideas-unique-tech-gadgets&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;The Verge 最喜欢的 100 美元以下节日礼物&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge. com/23951136/gifts-under-100-best-cheap-tech-ideas-2023-budget&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;The Verge 最喜欢的 50 美元以下节日礼物&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www. theverge.com/23952179/tech-gifts-under-50-best-cheap-ideas-2023-budget&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;RX3Qyj&quot;>;不我们正在抱怨。毕竟，我们上次在亚马逊最近的 Prime Day 活动期间看到的许多出色优惠又回来了，为您提供了另一个节省费用的机会 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/all-new-amazon -fire-tv-stick-4k-max/dp/B0BP9SNVH9?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot; Sponsored nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;新款 Amazon Fire TV Stick 4K Max&lt;/a>;，&lt;a href =&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Lavender-Bloom-bundle-TP-Link-Smart/dp/B0CL8HJ3HD?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;赞助 nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Echo Pop&lt; /a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Kindle-Scribe-the-first-Kindle-for-reading-writing-journaling-and-sketching/dp/B09BS26B8B?tag=theverge02 -20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Kindle Scribe&lt;/a>; 等技术。在某些情况下，亚马逊甚至提供比 10 月份更大幅度的折扣，百思买、塔吉特和其他零售商也是如此。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;ZLzK4e&quot;>;在这里，我们进行了汇总最好的黑色星期五优惠...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23963020/black-friday-2023-amazon-deals-cyber-monday&quot;>;继续阅读……&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23963020/black-friday-2023-amazon-deals-cyber-monday" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23963020/black-friday-2023-amazon-deals-cyber-monday</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-17T08:45:00-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-17T08:45:00-05:00</updated><title>轮胎拯救了我们，也杀死了我们</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;概念图显示草从轮胎的打滑痕迹中生长出来，旨在展示未来拥有丰富的可持续制造轮胎的可能性。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/ThRa1cxlGgEtduIhQ6q6-iREisk=/0x0:2040x136